-- Inmet Mining Pays $552M for Leucadia Stake in Cobre Las Cruces in Spain
-- B y   T i m   S m i t h
-- 2010-11-30T04:35:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-30/inmet-mining-pays-552m-for-leucadia-stake-in-cobre-las-cruces-in-spain.html
Inmet Mining Corp. will pay $552
million to Leucadia National Corp. for its 30 percent stake in
the Cobre Las Cruces copper mine, according to a regulatory
filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
